e,Fungi,provides,a,database,that,integrates,data,on,multiple,fungal,genomes,including,fungi,and,oomycetes,It,does,so,in,such,a,way,as,to,facilitate,the,systematic,comparative,study,of,those,genomes,allowing,less,well,understood,species,to,be,studied,with,reference,to,model,organisms,with,more,fully,explored,functional,characteristics,It,also,offers,information,and,search,methods,to,help,researchers,conduct,studies,on,the,pathogenicity,the,ability,to,cause,disease,in,an,animal,or,plant,host,and,evolution,of,fungal,organisms